{
  "id": "adv_event_2512_01_03",
  "title": "ドタバタ！？トラブルクリスマス！ 3話 聖夜の発明品",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "アイドルとファンの想いが相乗効果となって",
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_03-rei001.wav",
      "text": "ライブ会場に膨大なエネルギーを生み出していた……？",
      "startTime": 4.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "そのエネルギーを使えば",
      "startTime": 8.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_03-rio001.wav",
      "text": "貴方達は元の世界に帰れるかもしれないのね？",
      "startTime": 10.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "lala",
      "speakerName": "ララ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-lala.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "うん！　だから、ライブ中にエネルギーを回収出来る",
      "startTime": 13.9962355932,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "lala",
      "speakerName": "ララ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-lala.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_03-lala001.wav",
      "text": "ように、みんなの衣装を改造させてもらえないかな？",
      "startTime": 17.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "私達の衣装を！？　あなた達の言ってることは",
      "startTime": 21.6962361019,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_03-rui001.wav",
      "text": "分かるけど、いつも使ってる衣装はちょっと……",
      "startTime": 25.3666671753,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "確かにそうですよね。……あ、そうだ！　ちょうど",
      "startTime": 29.1629034043,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_03-kkr001.wav",
      "text": "今作ってるクリスマス衣装を改造するのはどうですか？",
      "startTime": 33.9000005086,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "それなら可能かもしれないわね",
      "startTime": 37.929570071,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_03-rui002.wav",
      "text": "デザインはまだ確定していなかったし",
      "startTime": 40.633333842,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kyui",
      "speakerName": "古手川唯",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kyui.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "お願い、瑠依さん。これは元の世界に帰るために",
      "startTime": 43.829570071,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kyui",
      "speakerName": "古手川唯",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kyui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_03-kyui001.wav",
      "text": "必要なの。協力してくれないかしら？",
      "startTime": 47.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "……分かったわ。そのかわり、あなた達には",
      "startTime": 50.9295718511,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_03-rui003.wav",
      "text": "ライブの準備を手伝ってもらってもいいかしら？",
      "startTime": 54.3666689555,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yami",
      "speakerName": "金色の闇",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yami.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "分かりました",
      "startTime": 57.2295718511,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yami",
      "speakerName": "金色の闇",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yami.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_03-yami001.wav",
      "text": "私達に出来ることなら、なんでも言って下さい",
      "startTime": 59.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "それなら、せっかくだから、モモさん達も衣装を着て",
      "startTime": 63.0295675277,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_03-smr001.wav",
      "text": "一緒にステージに立ちませんか？",
      "startTime": 67.166664632,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kyui",
      "speakerName": "古手川唯",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kyui.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ええっ！？",
      "startTime": 69.6962341944,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kyui",
      "speakerName": "古手川唯",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kyui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_03-kyui002.wav",
      "text": "私達がステージで歌うなんて無理よ",
      "startTime": 70.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yami",
      "speakerName": "金色の闇",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yami.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "効率はいいですね。改造衣装を着た人の数が多いほど",
      "startTime": 74.0295690535,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yami",
      "speakerName": "金色の闇",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yami.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_03-yami002.wav",
      "text": "エネルギーを早く回収出来ます",
      "startTime": 78.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "momo",
      "speakerName": "モモ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-momo.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "それに、サプライズゲストでライブが盛り上がれば",
      "startTime": 81.4629161196,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "momo",
      "speakerName": "モモ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-momo.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_03-momo001.wav",
      "text": "より多くのエネルギーが発生するかもしれないですね",
      "startTime": 84.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "つまり、大量のエネルギーを一気に集めるには",
      "startTime": 88.7295873639,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_03-rui004.wav",
      "text": "あなた達もステージに立った方がいいということね",
      "startTime": 92.5333511349,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "lala",
      "speakerName": "ララ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-lala.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_03-lala002.wav",
      "text": "何より、みんなで歌った方が楽しいよ！",
      "startTime": 96.0295873639,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kyui",
      "speakerName": "古手川唯",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kyui.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "……仕方ないわね。これも元の世界に帰るためよ",
      "startTime": 99.8629237489,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kyui",
      "speakerName": "古手川唯",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kyui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_03-kyui003.wav",
      "text": "私も改造した衣装を着てステージに立つわ",
      "startTime": 105.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "でも、急に四人も増えて衣装作りは間に合うの？",
      "startTime": 109.0629166282,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_03-rei002.wav",
      "text": "材料だって私達の分しか用意してないだろうし……",
      "startTime": 113.4333470658,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "確かに、今から追加で四人分の材料を確保するのは",
      "startTime": 117.7962499615,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_03-rio002.wav",
      "text": "難しいかもしれないわね",
      "startTime": 122.1000137325,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "momo",
      "speakerName": "モモ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-momo.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "だったら、少ない材料でも作れる衣装に",
      "startTime": 124.5652550377,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "momo",
      "speakerName": "モモ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-momo.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_03-momo002.wav",
      "text": "デザインを変更してみるのはどうですか？",
      "startTime": 128.5666697185,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "モモちゃん、ナイスアイデアです！　衣装の布面積を",
      "startTime": 131.8652682619,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_03-kkr002.wav",
      "text": "半分に削れば五人分の材料で九人分作れますね！",
      "startTime": 136.1333633419,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "衣装の布面積が半分に……",
      "startTime": 141.3319349286,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_03-rio003.wav",
      "text": "冬なのにやたら肌の露出が多いサンタになりそうね",
      "startTime": 145.0333633419,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kyui",
      "speakerName": "古手川唯",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kyui.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "は、肌の露出は抑えめにしてよ！？",
      "startTime": 149.5436351456,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kyui",
      "speakerName": "古手川唯",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kyui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_03-kyui004.wav",
